title: Bejeweled 2 Deluxe
description:
Release Information:

  Escape to the gorgeous planetary vistas of Bejeweled 2, where sparkling
  gems burst into points when you match three or more. With explosive new
  jewels and dazzling special effects, Bejeweled 2 is more wildly addictive
  than ever before.

  Beautiful high-resolution graphics

  Four entrancing game modes - Classic, Action, Puzzle and Endless

  Over 80 mind-warping puzzles

  Earn high scores with cascades and combos
